&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Band 2 &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Full Time – 37.5 hours a week&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic and motivated individual to be an integral part of the Paediatric Intensive Care team. You will be responsible for ensuring a clean, safe and comfortable environment. To work with Support Services and coordinate the delivery of catering, cleaning and minor maintenance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Previous experience is essential and good organisation skills. You will need to have good interpersonal skills and be computer aware. You will need to have the ability to work independently and as part multi-disciplinary team&lt;/p&gt;
